snippet.title: Ghost Recon Predator - Launch Trailer [Europe]
snippet.description: More videos on http://www.ghostrecon.com. Deep inside the jungle, use advanced tactics, electronic warfare tools and massive firepower to defeat your enemies. Play solo or with up to two other players in coop.
